name: NSLayoutManager.TypesetterBehavior
desc: Constants that determine the layout manager's behavior during layout.

items.name: case latestBehavior
items.desc: The current typesetter behavior in the current operating system.

items.name: case originalBehavior
items.desc: The original typesetter behavior, as shipped with macOS 10.1 and earlier.

items.name: case behavior_10_2_WithCompatibility
items.desc: The macOS 10.2 typesetting behavior that is still compatible with the original typesetter behavior.

items.name: case behavior_10_2
items.desc: The typesetter behavior introduced in macOS 10.2.

items.name: case behavior_10_3
items.desc: The typesetter behavior introduced in macOS 10.3.

items.name: case behavior_10_4
items.desc: The typesetter behavior introduced in macOS 10.4.
